Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.37,0:00:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是汐宫栞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.37,0:00:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正被一种巨大而又莫名其妙的「怪异」缠身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.90,0:00:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种诡异的感觉时刻困扰着我的身心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.59,0:00:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我不敢放松丝毫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.87,0:00:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞高祭用的影印本小说写好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.66,0:00:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还  还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的「一点」也太久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.42,0:00:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是后天早上还不能提交上来  那就不用你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.06,0:00:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我其实已经有所察觉  这种「怪异」的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.57,0:00:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是被世上的普通男女称为恋  恋…恋爱的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.72,0:00:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该没错…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:01:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在故事中描述得有时甜蜜  有时可爱  有时悲伤的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.33,0:01:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我的感受却不是上面的任何一种
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.84,0:01:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,介入我的小说之中的那个他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.91,0:01:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟男人搂搂抱抱的那个他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男扮女装还大笑不止的那个他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.36,0:01:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他和当初我在图书馆闭关不出时拯救了我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.29,0:01:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是同一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.49,0:01:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来这还真是够离谱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.45,0:01:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一个邂逅的男人竟然是那种…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒错  变态  女装癖的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.32,0:01:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你让我怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.64,0:01:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而让我最无法原谅的是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.97,0:01:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那男人是个不守承诺的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明说好了会来看我写的小说的续章
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天我一整天都在等他却没见人来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.61,0:01:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果只是个倒错变态男的话还有得救
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.41,0:01:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可一个不守承诺的倒错变态男根本无可救药
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.12,0:02:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是和那样的男人…接吻了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.34,0:02:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  直到不久前我对这事一点印象都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我难道是个将人生中初次接吻这种大事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都轻易忘掉的大呆瓜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.11,0:02:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是这女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是从哪进来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道是哪来的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是汐宫栞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正被一种莫名其妙的「怪异」缠身
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邂逅的神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我去死一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:07.53,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Look up at the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:10.16,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Like a bird without wings
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:12.56,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}If you want to fly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:15.92,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Feel your breeze, release yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:17.44,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Why do you sigh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:20.03,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Just count your blessings
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:22.39,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Every time you try
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:29.37,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Find something, believe yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:39.89,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}My mission is gonna be a tough one
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.89,0:03:42.49,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I know it's not a game anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:45.55,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I swear that I'll never fail again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:48.77,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}'Cuz don't wanna regret anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:51.27,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Can you hear I'm calling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.55,0:03:53.98,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I just wanna feel you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.37,0:03:56.81,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Don't forget to remember
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:59.53,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}So please remember
